## Sensitive Data

- **Sensitive data types**: {{domain.sensitive_data}}
- **Compliance frameworks**: {{domain.compliance}}
- Never log sensitive data fields
- Never expose sensitive data in error messages or API responses

## Quality Checklist

- [ ] Every endpoint has the full middleware chain
- [ ] Frontend checks privileges before rendering protected UI
{{#if patterns.isolation.enabled}}
- [ ] Queries filter by `{{patterns.isolation.field}}`
{{/if}}
- [ ] Audit trail for sensitive data changes
- [ ] No sensitive data in logs or error responses

